    "aliases": [
      "Blame",
      "Calumniation",
      "Rebuke",
      "Reprimand",
      "Reproof"
    ],
    "text": "If one sees himself\ncensured by a prophet, a saint, a godly person, or a bosom friend in a dream, it\nmeans repentance from sin, refraining from walking the avenues of error and\ntemptation. Censure in a dream also signifies love and compassion. If one\nrebukes himself in a dream, it means that he had indulged in a wrongdoing\nwhich he regrets and that he is blaming himself for it.",
