  "counting": {
    "aliases": [
      "Add",
      "Calculate",
      "Enumerate",
      "Number"
    ],
    "text": "Counting apples in a dream\nmeans counting money. Counting up to the number one hundred, five thousand\nor twenty thousand in a dream signifies victory against one's enemy. Counting\nup to the number seven or eight means distress or pressures. Counting up to the\nnumber nine in a dream means adversities and joining the company of corrupt\nand evil people. Counting up to the number ten in a dream means completing\na project, or it could mean attending the pilgrimage in Mecca. Counting up to\nthe number forty in a dream means anticipating the fulfillment of a promise.\nCounting up to the number thirty in a dream means promising someone the\nimpossible or telling a lie. The number one in a dream signifies uniqueness,\nsuperiority, having the leading edge in knowledge, money, prosperity, marriage, child, or it could mean languor, solitude or liking to be alone or cessation\nof activities. The number one in a dream also represents the truth or God\nAlmighty Who has no partner, associate or equal. The number two means help\nagainst one's enemy. The number three signifies fulfillment of a promise. The\nnumber four means a pilgrimage to Mecca. The number five means doubt and\nweakness of one's faith. Perhaps the number six also means victory against one's\nenemy or establishing a proof of guilt against one's adversaries. Counting up to\nnumber seven or eight in a dream has negative connotations. Counting up to\nnumber ten in a dream could mean atonement for one's sins. If one sees himself\nin a dream counting money coins that has the name of God inscribed on it in a\ndream, it means that he celebrates God's praises and glorifies His Name. If one\nsees himself in a dream counting large denomination of money that has the\nName of God Almighty written on it, it means acquiring knowledge. If the money\ncoins or the banknotes are designed with images or portray the picture of known\npeople in the dream, then they mean engaging in innovation, religious innovation,\nfalsehood or polytheism. Counting pearls in a dream means reading the Qur'an.\nCounting gems in a dream means learning wisdom or acquiring knowledge at\nthe hand of a gnostic. Counting beads in a dream means getting involved in\npeople's business, using obscene language, or fornication. Counting sheep in a\ndream means counting money or counting one's children. Counting cows in a\ndream means longevity or going through a long and difficult times. If a farmer\nsees himself counting camels in a dream, it means rain and a good harvest.\nCounting buffaloes in a dream means hardships and toiling in one's life.",
    "related_entries": [
      "money"
    ],
    "redirect": null,
    "lookup_aliases": {
      "en": [
        "number",
        "enumerate",
        "calculate",
        "counting",
        "add"
      ],
      "fr": [
        "compter",
        "comptage"
      ],
      "ar": [
        "عد",
        "حساب"
      ],
      "tr": [
        "sayma"
      ],
      "de": [
        "zählen"
      ]
    }
  },
