    "aliases": [
      "Planet",
      "Policeman"
    ],
    "text": "The planet Mercury in a dream represents people\nof authority, writers, commanders, secretary of state, minister, traveling from\none country to another, distress, adversities, or fights. If in wakefulness the\nMoon and Mercury are appearing simultaneously in the skies, then all dreams\nwill be false and one may have to face lies, poverty, scary news, murders, or\nrobberies. The planet Mercury in a dream also represents a policeman.",
