    "text": "A shoemaker in a dream represents\nsomeone who brings peace and unity between adversaries, a lawyer, a peacemaker, a scholar or a shaikh who specializes in jurisprudence relating to\ninheritance laws. A shoemaker in a dream has many meanings. Some shoemakers\nspecialize in repairing women's shoes. In that case, in a dream, he represents\na pimp or a brothel owner. As for those specializing in men's shoes, seeing him\nin a dream means travel, or employing people to work in one's business.",
