    "aliases": [
      "Shake",
      "Shiver",
      "Tremor"
    ],
    "text": "Seeing one's head trembling in a dream means\ngaining honor and rising in station. If one's righ t hand trembles or shakes in a\ndream, it means difficulties in earning his livelihood. If one's right leg trembles\nin a dream, it means profits from one's family or clan. If one's left leg trembles\nin a dream, it means business losses. The same applies to the trembling or the\nshocking of any part of one's body. (See Body'; Tremor)",
