    "aliases": [],
    "text": "In a dream, the walls of a city represent strong men, a strong\nruler, or a treasurer who is concerned about guarding the interests of his people.\nThe walls of a city in a dream also represent the most pious and devout\nworshiper in that city, its most renowned men of knowledge, its supremejustice,\nor its just ruler. Seeing the walls of a city in a dream also meansjoy, festivities\nand celebrations.",
