    "aliases": [
      "Astray",
      "Error",
      "Lost"
    ],
    "text": "Walking on a straight highway and still losing\none's way in a dream means deviating from the path of truth. If the road in the\ndream is twisted or curved, then it means allurement, trespassing, misguidance,\nor erring from God's path, or it could mean seeking a way out of error. If one is\nlost in the dream, it means that he will become heedless, and ifhe finds his way\nthereafter, it means that he will receive someone's guidance and accept it.",
