    "aliases": [],
    "text": "In a dream, women represent the world, its glitters and pleasures. If one\nsees women coming toward him in a dream, it means his success in the world.\nIf they walk away from him in the dream, it means his poverty in the world.\nSitting content in the company of women in a dream means lack of work.",
