    "aliases": [
      "Roll up",
      "Swathe"
    ],
    "text": "In a dream, a wrap represents one's limbs. To wrap\nup something in a dream means turning the page on something, closing a book,\nretracing one's steps, winding up a conversation, or controlling the spread of a\nrumor.",
